    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Hi, thanks for reporting this. It seems to happen even when the widget is not inside a portal, as a simple state change seems to undo active refinements. We'll look into this and let you know once we have a fix.\r\n\r\nEDIT: Nevermind, I haven't noticed you inline the `transformItems` method, which makes the component unstable. You should declare your method outside of your component, as shown in the API reference: https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/widgets/refinement-list/react/#widget-param-transformitems.",
