    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Thank you for the quick reply @dhayab ! Declaring `transformItems` outside of the component does indeed avoid the issue. It looks like wrapping the function in `useCallback` also works if we need to declare the function _inside_ the component (in the case where we need access to other component state maybe?)",
